Disk World creator help
add_member

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_member -  This function allows you to add a member to a group.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_member(string name,
object person)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the group
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the person you're adding
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 if the group doesn't exist or person is
   already a member
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function allows you to add a member to a group.

.EP

